 the spring of each year  The Roberts Medal  Established in honor of John W  and Jane M  Roberts to recognize their lifelong interest in the American free enterprise system and their unswerving support for the Department of Economics and Business  The medal recognizes the top standing by an economics and business major in the graduating class  Class of 2008  Eric J  Hunter Class of 2009   Jacob N  Rochester Class of 2010   Daniel L  Welsh Class of 2011   Adam T  Kruithof Class of 2012   Michael A  Shafer Class of 2013   Simone R  Jiminez Class of 2014   Chih Yuan Chen   The Wheat Medal  Established in honor of James Clifton Wheat  Jr  Class of 1941  to acknowledge his lifelong interest in economics and business studies at VMI  and his leadership in the VMI Foundation s Economics Fund Drive  1969 1970  Up until the spring of 2008  the medal recognized excellence in economics studies by an Economics and Business major in the graduating class  Currently  the medal recognizes outstanding performance on the Major Field Test Business by an economics and business major in the graduating class  Class of 1971  Louis J  Cowardin  Jr  Class of 1972   Steven W  Palmer Class of 1973   Douglas K  Baumgardner Class of 1974   Albert J  Graham  III Class of 1975   Robert A  Lane Class of 1976   Kurt P  Luckenbill Class of 1977   Charles T  Floyd Class of 1978   Ivan A  Moore  Jr  Class of 1979   Nicholas C  Kepf Class of 1980   Robert B  Gore Class of 1981   Jeffrey M  Gill Class of 1982   Gordon R  Hammock Class of 1983   John C  Manning Class of 1984   Ralph A  Foertsch Class of 1985   Daniel W  Murphy Class of 1986   Joseph J  Thompson  III Class of 1987   Kevin P  Sincavage Class of 1988   Trent H  Beck Class of 1989   Thomas D  Shelton Class of 1990   John B  Cabell Class of 1991   Kyle A  Bryan Class of 1992   David F  Brugger Class of 1993   Troy D  Spencer Class of 1994   Nicolas B  Schweizer Class of 1995   Jeremy Ingram Class of 1996   John D  Adams Class of 1997   David O